What are you doing, Dad?

00:36:01.559 --> 00:36:03.059 line:93%
I am going home.

00:36:05.028 --> 00:36:06.669 line:93%
The doctor said you have to stay here...

00:36:06.669 --> 00:36:08.568 line:93%
until the results come out.

00:36:08.628 --> 00:36:11.398 line:93%
You've become weak, so you need to stay here.

00:36:11.398 --> 00:36:13.108 line:93%
I said I'm okay.

00:36:13.238 --> 00:36:15.169 line:93%
Dad, what's wrong with you?

00:36:16.479 --> 00:36:17.878 line:93%
Let's talk at home.

00:36:17.939 --> 00:36:19.639 line:93%
Please, Honey.

00:36:26.278 --> 00:36:27.718 line:93%
I will fix the bed for you.

00:36:28.648 --> 00:36:30.289 line:93%
I will take some rest.

00:36:30.818 --> 00:36:32.459 line:93%
You should all go now.

00:36:35.189 --> 00:36:37.698 line:93%
How can we go when you're unwell?

00:36:38.128 --> 00:36:41.568 line:93%
Where were you going with your luggage?

00:36:42.229 --> 00:36:44.238 line:93%
The training has been moved forward,

00:36:44.238 --> 00:36:46.269 line:93%
so I was leaving early.

00:36:46.568 --> 00:36:48.269 line:93%
I wrote it here.

00:36:49.068 --> 00:36:50.979 line:93%
You're undernourished.

00:36:51.079 --> 00:36:52.608 line:93%
You can't go deep-sea fishing like that.

00:36:52.608 --> 00:36:54.349 line:93%
You even collapsed in the street.

00:36:54.448 --> 00:36:56.519 line:93%
I heard you even threw up blood.

00:36:56.948 --> 00:36:58.448 line:93%
You're not going deep-sea fishing.

00:36:59.818 --> 00:37:00.948 line:93%
I called them.

00:37:02.318 --> 00:37:04.419 line:93%
Who? Who did you call?

00:37:04.419 --> 00:37:05.488 line:93%
How did you know who to call?

00:37:05.488 --> 00:37:08.059 line:93%
I checked all the deep-sea fishing vessels in Busan.

00:37:08.959 --> 00:37:10.329 line:93%
You weren't on the list.

00:37:11.298 --> 00:37:13.169 line:93%
You cancelled on the agency....

00:37:13.169 --> 00:37:14.468 line:93%
and said you won't go.

00:37:16.128 --> 00:37:18.439 line:93%
If it's not that you're going deep-sea fishing,

00:37:18.869 --> 00:37:20.838 line:93%
