Then you knew about this?

00:38:29.809 --> 00:38:32.238 line:93%
Dad, what does that mean?

00:38:32.238 --> 00:38:33.508 line:93%
Why would you not get treatment?

00:38:34.479 --> 00:38:36.209 line:93%
Do you want to just die like this?

00:38:37.479 --> 00:38:38.579 line:93%
What's wrong with that?

00:38:38.718 --> 00:38:40.048 line:93%
- Dad. - Dad.

