Not even for a single day.

00:38:56.499 --> 00:38:58.939 line:93%
So I'll die the way I want.

00:38:59.738 --> 00:39:01.309 line:93%
That's ridiculous.

00:39:01.738 --> 00:39:04.079 line:93%
How could you say such a thing?

00:39:04.079 --> 00:39:05.709 line:93%
What about us?

