What should we do when you say that?

00:39:07.079 --> 00:39:08.778 line:93%
Don't you even care about us?

00:39:09.108 --> 00:39:10.548 line:93%
Yes, I won't care about you.

00:39:11.178 --> 00:39:12.749 line:93%
I'm glad I'm dying.

00:39:12.749 --> 00:39:14.488 line:93%
