00:39:14.849 --> 00:39:16.619 line:93%
I couldn't choose how to live my life,

00:39:17.358 --> 00:39:18.718 line:93%
but I'll choose how to die.

00:39:19.389 --> 00:39:21.959 line:93%
Were you going to die alone?

00:39:22.428 --> 00:39:25.159 line:93%
Is that why you were leaving alone like that?

00:39:25.159 --> 00:39:26.499 line:93%
I told you.

00:39:26.499 --> 00:39:28.468 line:93%
I'll live my own life from now on.

00:39:28.968 --> 00:39:31.099 line:93%
Dad, how could you say that?

00:39:31.099 --> 00:39:32.769 line:93%
Why would you only care about you?

00:39:32.769 --> 00:39:35.409 line:93%
He's right. Don't you even care about your children?

00:39:37.409 --> 00:39:38.878 line:93%
What's so wrong not to care about them?

00:39:39.639 --> 00:39:41.608 line:93%
Why can't I care only about me?

00:39:47.419 --> 00:39:49.318 line:93%
I've lived my entire life for my family.

00:39:49.548 --> 00:39:52.659 line:93%
Whether I was good or not, I lived for my family.

00:39:53.159 --> 00:39:54.729 line:93%
Now, I want to live...

00:39:55.428 --> 00:39:56.528 line:93%
my life...

00:39:56.528 --> 00:39:58.229 line:93%
the way I want to.

00:39:58.229 --> 00:39:59.999 line:93%
Why would you blame me for that?

00:40:00.769 --> 00:40:02.198 line:93%
Did I do you any harm?

00:40:02.898 --> 00:40:04.369 line:93%
Did I cause you any trouble?

00:40:07.139 --> 00:40:08.269 line:93%
Do you want us...

00:40:09.878 --> 00:40:11.108 line:93%
to just watch you...

00:40:11.678 --> 00:40:13.148 line:93%
die like that?

00:40:13.749 --> 00:40:17.318 line:93%
It will only break your children's hearts.

00:40:17.749 --> 00:40:20.619 line:93%
Dad, you're being too selfish.

00:40:20.988 --> 00:40:22.189 line:93%
I don't care.

00:40:23.289 --> 00:40:24.988 line:93%
Even if you regret it...

00:40:24.988 --> 00:40:27.358 line:93%
and become remorseful after I die,

00:40:27.758 --> 00:40:30.229 line:93%
I don't care about it. It's none of my business.

00:40:31.128 --> 00:40:32.128 line:93%
Tae Soo.

00:40:33.798 --> 00:40:35.698 line:93%
It's because I want to stop everything now.

00:40:36.539 --> 00:40:38.198 line:93%
I want to stop.

00:40:39.269 --> 00:40:40.568 line:93%
It's okay not to live...

00:40:40.568 --> 00:40:42.439 line:93%
if I have no reason to live.

