It's not that I'm committing suicide.

00:40:46.178 --> 00:40:48.249 line:93%
They are just calling me from up above.

00:40:49.209 --> 00:40:50.749 line:93%
It's that simple to me.

00:41:01.729 --> 00:41:02.988 line:93%
I want to rest.

00:41:04.329 --> 00:41:05.798 line:93%
I want to rest now.

00:41:06.628 --> 00:41:07.669 line:93%
You guys...

00:41:08.829 --> 00:41:10.698 line:93%
will live your own life.

00:41:11.639 --> 00:41:13.409 line:93%
That's what children do.

00:41:35.588 --> 00:41:36.959 line:93%
Now, I want...

00:41:38.928 --> 00:41:40.499 line:93%
to quit everything.

00:42:10.959 --> 00:42:12.059 line:93%
Your dad...

00:42:14.028 --> 00:42:15.468 line:93%
knew about it.

00:42:17.068 --> 00:42:18.468 line:93%
He knew it.

00:42:20.968 --> 00:42:23.139 line:93%
What did the doctor say?

00:42:26.209 --> 00:42:28.249 line:93%
He has some symptoms,

00:42:28.278 --> 00:42:29.778 line:93%
and his family has...

00:42:29.778 --> 00:42:31.378 line:93%
a history of stomach cancer.

00:42:31.718 --> 00:42:33.818 line:93%
So there's a possibility of stomach cancer.

00:42:35.419 --> 00:42:38.119 line:93%
But we should wait for the biopsy results.

00:42:39.189 --> 00:42:41.258 line:93%
He wasn't like that before.

00:42:44.159 --> 00:42:46.128 line:93%
He only cared about his family.

00:42:48.068 --> 00:42:49.838 line:93%
But now, he wants to die alone?

00:42:52.669 --> 00:42:53.709 line:93%
Ji An.

00:42:55.539 --> 00:42:56.738 line:93%
Is that really...

00:42:58.139 --> 00:42:59.508 line:93%
what Dad meant?

00:43:00.979 --> 00:43:03.519 line:93%
Did he mean that he wants to die alone?

00:43:04.249 --> 00:43:06.278 line:93%
Dad knew, but he lied to all of us,

00:43:07.818 --> 00:43:08.849 line:93%
didn't he?

00:43:11.218 --> 00:43:13.729 line:93%
He even left a will to me the other day.

00:43:14.488 --> 00:43:15.889 line:93%
It was his will.

00:43:17.258 --> 00:43:18.499 line:93%
What should we do?

00:43:20.568 --> 00:43:22.298 line:93%
We've seen him so far.

00:43:23.269 --> 00:43:25.999 line:93%
He must've been in so much pain alone.

00:43:30.409 --> 00:43:33.178 line:93%
I didn't know he'd be like that.

00:43:35.048 --> 00:43:36.479 line:93%
Just because I know...

