doesn't mean I didn't feel miserable.

00:43:41.119 --> 00:43:43.218 line:93%
So I cowed around you.

00:43:44.059 --> 00:43:45.919 line:93%
I pretended not to care and smiled along, but...

00:43:45.919 --> 00:43:48.588 line:93%
now, I'm sick of tiptoeing around you all the time.

00:43:49.959 --> 00:43:51.959 line:93%
If he's that bad...

00:43:55.229 --> 00:43:57.398 line:93%
Grandma had a surgery in stage three, right?

00:43:58.639 --> 00:44:01.169 line:93%
Why would you all think he has stomach cancer?

00:44:01.338 --> 00:44:02.939 line:93%
We don't know yet.

00:44:07.508 --> 00:44:08.648 line:93%
For now, we should...

00:44:09.349 --> 00:44:11.579 line:93%
wait until the results are out tomorrow.

00:44:12.218 --> 00:44:14.119 line:93%
And we should persuade him to get treatment then.

00:44:14.548 --> 00:44:16.218 line:93%
Is he doing this because of money?

00:44:17.019 --> 00:44:18.289 line:93%
Because of the hospital bills?

00:44:22.789 --> 00:44:24.099 line:93%
Gosh, this is irritating.

00:44:25.798 --> 00:44:26.869 line:93%
No.

00:44:27.869 --> 00:44:29.999 line:93%
He can't die already.

00:44:31.269 --> 00:44:32.269 line:93%
I should get going.

00:44:38.979 --> 00:44:40.878 line:93%
Soo A doesn't know about this yet, right?

00:44:43.479 --> 00:44:45.419 line:93%
Does the training end this week?

00:44:45.479 --> 00:44:47.919 line:93%
Don't tell her before she comes back.

00:44:47.919 --> 00:44:49.218 line:93%
She'd only be depressed.

00:44:50.059 --> 00:44:54.088 line:93%
Well, what should we do with Ji Soo?

00:44:57.159 --> 00:44:58.798 line:93%
Don't tell her...

00:44:58.798 --> 00:44:59.898 line:93%
until the results are out.

