You were going to do it,

00:45:23.559 --> 00:45:25.588 line:93%
but I stopped you.

00:45:25.588 --> 00:45:28.389 line:93%
That means I asked you out first.

00:45:29.528 --> 00:45:31.459 line:93%
Gosh, Hyuk.

00:45:33.369 --> 00:45:36.499 line:93%
You didn't know he'd be so romantic and tough, right?

00:45:37.338 --> 00:45:39.439 line:93%
I hope we will get along well.

