I was going to say the same thing.

00:45:42.738 --> 00:45:44.809 line:93%
I've made sustained efforts...

00:45:44.809 --> 00:45:47.849 line:93%
to make them a couple. Yes.

00:45:47.849 --> 00:45:49.878 line:93%
I sent you two to Incheon together, right?

00:45:49.878 --> 00:45:51.579 line:93%
I even made him buy her lunch.

00:45:51.579 --> 00:45:53.148 line:93%
Most importantly,

00:45:53.148 --> 00:45:55.849 line:93%
I told her everything about women in his life.

00:45:56.189 --> 00:45:58.559 line:93%
My goodness. I'm sorry.

