Let's go.

00:50:52.948 --> 00:50:53.948 line:93%
Hey!

00:50:57.358 --> 00:51:02.189 line:93%
Show me the money, money. Money...

00:51:02.628 --> 00:51:05.358 line:93%
I wish I had lots of money

00:51:06.468 --> 00:51:08.229 line:93%
Money, money

00:51:08.229 --> 00:51:09.738 line:93%
Be quiet.

