00:54:20.988 --> 00:54:22.858 line:93%
You can't do that here.

00:54:23.198 --> 00:54:24.499 line:93%
It's a yellow card. Once more and it's a red.

00:54:24.628 --> 00:54:26.968 line:93%
If you do it again, it'll be a red card.

00:54:27.329 --> 00:54:28.669 line:93%
You'll get out right away.

00:54:31.738 --> 00:54:33.338 line:93%
Who did what at night?

00:54:45.878 --> 00:54:47.088 line:93%
It wasn't a dream?

00:54:49.389 --> 00:54:51.318 line:93%
Did she nurse me all night?

00:55:01.999 --> 00:55:03.169 line:93%
Should family members...

00:55:04.039 --> 00:55:05.769 line:93%
always do everything together?

00:55:06.539 --> 00:55:10.709 line:93%
But you should at least give us a chance.

00:55:11.278 --> 00:55:13.508 line:93%
You should at least give us a chance.

00:55:14.048 --> 00:55:16.619 line:93%
I want to be alone without my family now.

00:55:17.648 --> 00:55:19.689 line:93%
Don't think about your family now.

00:55:20.419 --> 00:55:22.249 line:93%
Do whatever makes you happy.

00:55:24.559 --> 00:55:26.159 line:93%
Dad...

00:55:40.639 --> 00:55:42.539 line:93%
How can he say he wants to die...

00:55:43.008 --> 00:55:44.508 line:93%
so nonchalantly?

00:55:49.778 --> 00:55:51.178 line:93%
I'll deal with it.

00:55:51.178 --> 00:55:53.588 line:93%
I'm no longer a child.

00:55:53.818 --> 00:55:54.889 line:93%
Stop it.

00:55:55.318 --> 00:55:57.419 line:93%
You don't know why I'm like this.

00:55:58.019 --> 00:55:59.588 line:93%
It's not like your times.

00:55:59.588 --> 00:56:00.588 line:93%
I won't do...

00:56:01.229 --> 00:56:02.789 line:93%
anything I'll regret.

00:56:03.028 --> 00:56:04.959 line:93%
How could you do that?

00:56:05.758 --> 00:56:07.128 line:93%
Are you both crazy?

00:56:07.398 --> 00:56:08.628 line:93%
How could you...

00:56:09.499 --> 00:56:11.898 line:93%
How could you do something like that?

00:56:12.139 --> 00:56:15.769 line:93%
Did it never occur to you...

00:56:15.869 --> 00:56:19.678 line:93%
to ask why we did that and what we were thinking?

00:56:19.849 --> 00:56:21.278 line:93%
What's there to hear?

00:56:22.309 --> 00:56:24.749 line:93%
Can anything you say be enough of an excuse?

00:56:56.648 --> 00:56:57.678 line:93%
A baby's bracelet?

00:57:00.588 --> 00:57:01.718 line:93%
How did he know?

00:57:11.858 --> 00:57:12.858 line:93%
Soo A.

00:57:13.729 --> 00:57:16.568 line:93%
It bothered me that I didn't buy you...

00:57:16.599 --> 00:57:18.439 line:93%
any jewelry when you got married.

00:57:19.968 --> 00:57:22.909 line:93%
I'm sorry to give you this as I leave.

00:57:23.979 --> 00:57:26.878 line:93%
And there are times in life...

00:57:26.878 --> 00:57:28.979 line:93%
when you will fall.

00:57:29.749 --> 00:57:32.778 line:93%
The thing to stop you from falling completely...

00:57:33.019 --> 00:57:34.718 line:93%
can be your children.

00:57:36.459 --> 00:57:38.818 line:93%
If you are blessed with such a child,

00:57:39.459 --> 00:57:40.628 line:93%
give them this.

00:57:46.028 --> 00:57:47.068 line:93%
Dad...

00:58:10.789 --> 00:58:11.858 line:93%
Are you asleep?

00:58:20.068 --> 00:58:21.169 line:93%
Are you asleep?

00:58:22.499 --> 00:58:23.968 line:93%
Yes, I am.

00:58:26.409 --> 00:58:27.769 line:93%
We need to talk.

00:58:28.939 --> 00:58:30.579 line:93%
Just go to sleep.

00:58:35.479 --> 00:58:37.318 line:93%
How can I sleep?

00:58:37.818 --> 00:58:39.378 line:93%
Do you think I can?

00:58:44.289 --> 00:58:45.419 line:93%
I'm sorry.

00:58:48.159 --> 00:58:49.798 line:93%
I did everything wrong.

00:58:51.059 --> 00:58:52.428 line:93%
What did you do?

00:58:55.369 --> 00:58:58.738 line:93%
I cornered you and forced Ji An away.

00:59:01.139 --> 00:59:04.209 line:93%
I also got a restaurant in return.

00:59:07.278 --> 00:59:09.309 line:93%
And I didn't even know you were sick.

00:59:11.378 --> 00:59:12.579 line:93%
I'm sorry.

00:59:15.988 --> 00:59:17.818 line:93%
I know how you feel now,

00:59:18.358 --> 00:59:20.289 line:93%
so will you do me a favor?

00:59:21.488 --> 00:59:22.488 line:93%
What?

00:59:24.099 --> 00:59:27.298 line:93%
Don't be a burden to the kids.

00:59:29.599 --> 00:59:32.439 line:93%
Will you stop saying that? You're scaring me.

00:59:33.968 --> 00:59:36.068 line:93%
I can't live without you.

00:59:36.338 --> 00:59:37.909 line:93%
I can't live alone.

00:59:39.579 --> 00:59:40.948 line:93%
These days,

00:59:41.948 --> 00:59:43.718 line:93%
young people can barely...

00:59:44.419 --> 00:59:47.749 line:93%
raise kids without their parents' help.

00:59:49.218 --> 00:59:51.119 line:93%
You're perfectly capable of working,

00:59:51.619 --> 00:59:53.358 line:93%
so leeching off your kids...

00:59:54.488 --> 00:59:56.028 line:93%
is just wrong.

00:59:57.198 --> 00:59:58.229 line:93%
Honey.

01:00:06.539 --> 01:00:07.838 line:93%
Everyone...

01:00:08.369 --> 01:00:10.878 line:93%
dies at some point.

01:00:12.378 --> 01:00:15.249 line:93%
I'm sorry I didn't keep the promise that...

01:00:15.979 --> 01:00:17.448 line:93%
I'd take good care of you,

01:00:18.548 --> 01:00:21.619 line:93%
but a married couple thrives on trust.

01:00:22.148 --> 01:00:24.619 line:93%
It's not just about living together.

01:00:29.358 --> 01:00:30.499 line:93%
I've...

01:00:31.428 --> 01:00:32.928 line:93%
settled everything.

01:00:34.198 --> 01:00:36.229 line:93%
I'm ready to go.

01:01:44.039 --> 01:01:45.599 line:93%
I'm off to live alone.

01:01:46.298 --> 01:01:48.439 line:93%
You'll get a call in time.

01:01:49.039 --> 01:01:51.278 line:93%
Don't worry about me.

01:01:55.778 --> 01:01:58.079 line:93%
Ji An. Ji Tae.

01:02:01.889 --> 01:02:02.919 line:93%
What?

01:02:02.919 --> 01:02:04.289 line:93%
Your dad's gone.

01:02:04.318 --> 01:02:05.758 line:93%
He left.

01:02:05.758 --> 01:02:06.758 line:93%
When?

01:02:07.028 --> 01:02:09.059 line:93%
Didn't you notice him leaving?

01:02:09.229 --> 01:02:11.999 line:93%
I stayed up until very late and dozed off.

01:02:11.999 --> 01:02:13.298 line:93%
That's when he left.

01:02:13.298 --> 01:02:15.229 line:93%
Did he take all his things?

01:02:15.229 --> 01:02:16.999 line:93%
He took his guitar too.

01:02:16.999 --> 01:02:19.198 line:93%
What should we do now?

01:02:19.599 --> 01:02:21.108 line:93%
I should've slept by him.

01:02:21.568 --> 01:02:22.639 line:93%
I should've watched him.

01:02:24.409 --> 01:02:26.548 line:93%
The phone is turned off.

01:02:26.548 --> 01:02:29.749 line:93%
Please leave a message after the tone.

01:03:19.628 --> 01:03:20.628 line:93%
Seo Ji An.

01:03:22.798 --> 01:03:25.068 line:93%
Were you in my room two nights ago?

01:03:28.008 --> 01:03:29.269 line:93%
Did you nurse me?

01:03:31.008 --> 01:03:32.338 line:93%
I brought you some medicine...

01:03:32.338 --> 01:03:33.778 line:93%
since I thought you'd need them.

01:03:33.809 --> 01:03:35.008 line:93%
Did you just leave that?

01:03:35.479 --> 01:03:37.148 line:93%
You wiped me with a wet cloth.

01:03:38.148 --> 01:03:39.689 line:93%
You had a bad fever.

01:03:39.689 --> 01:03:42.088 line:93%
Why do you care? You shouldn't care...

01:03:42.088 --> 01:03:44.159 line:93%
if I have a fever or even die by that fever.

01:03:44.159 --> 01:03:45.358 line:93%
You shouldn't care.

01:03:45.358 --> 01:03:47.428 line:93%
I did it as a housemate.

01:03:47.428 --> 01:03:49.289 line:93%
If anyone else were to be sick like that,

01:03:49.289 --> 01:03:50.829 line:93%
I'd have done the same.

01:03:51.358 --> 01:03:52.559 line:93%
You forgot.

01:03:52.959 --> 01:03:55.499 line:93%
I hate it when others invade my personal space.

01:03:55.968 --> 01:03:57.838 line:93%
Why are you still here?

01:03:58.669 --> 01:03:59.709 line:93%
Are you asking...

01:04:00.669 --> 01:04:02.409 line:93%
why I haven't gone home yet?

01:04:03.079 --> 01:04:04.079 line:93%
Yes.

01:04:05.278 --> 01:04:07.409 line:93%
Who said I'll go home if I end it with you?

01:04:10.849 --> 01:04:11.878 line:93%
I told you.

01:04:12.718 --> 01:04:14.648 line:93%
My independence isn't just about you.

01:04:17.459 --> 01:04:19.758 line:93%
I won't go home until I can stand on my own.

01:04:21.159 --> 01:04:24.028 line:93%
Seo Ji An, it's not about you now.

01:04:42.608 --> 01:04:45.079 line:93%
Why is she a mess if she slept at home?

01:04:48.988 --> 01:04:50.718 line:93%
It looked like she cried.

01:04:53.689 --> 01:04:56.128 line:93%
Mom, did you find Dad yet?

01:04:56.128 --> 01:04:57.698 line:93%
Not yet.

01:04:58.028 --> 01:05:00.798 line:93%
It's like he vanished into thin air or underground.

01:05:00.798 --> 01:05:02.669 line:93%
Then meet me at the hospital first.

01:06:09.968 --> 01:06:12.198 line:93%
Well, how are the results?

01:06:12.798 --> 01:06:15.369 line:93%
Seo Tae Soo doesn't have stomach cancer.

01:06:21.209 --> 01:06:24.079 line:93%
It's not cancer?

01:06:24.148 --> 01:06:27.818 line:93%
No. The biopsy results were negative.

01:06:27.988 --> 01:06:31.059 line:93%
Then how do you explain the vomiting,

01:06:31.289 --> 01:06:32.619 line:93%
stomach aches, and blood?

01:06:32.689 --> 01:06:34.088 line:93%
Well, there's something...

01:06:35.229 --> 01:06:38.358 line:93%
we call hypochondriasis.

01:06:38.358 --> 01:06:40.028 line:93%
People who worry too much...

01:06:40.269 --> 01:06:42.099 line:93%
that they might have cancer...

01:06:42.099 --> 01:06:45.269 line:93%
sometimes show the exact same symptoms.

01:06:45.698 --> 01:06:47.639 line:93%
Hypochondriasis?

01:06:48.309 --> 01:06:50.678 line:93%
But in his case,

01:06:51.278 --> 01:06:52.479 line:93%
it's different.

01:06:55.148 --> 01:06:56.619 line:93%
It's an imaginary cancer.

01:06:58.019 --> 01:07:00.419 line:93%
Imaginary cancer?

